[ File changes (patch level 2)
	D = Deleted.
	M = Modified.
	A = Added.

	M The Forgotten Server.exe
	M data/global.lua
]

[ Milestone (patch level 2)
	Fixed a crash when using health potions.
	Added three new optional parameters to doPlayerSendTextMessage (can be used for animated numbers): position, value and color.
	Updated global.lua with more message constants.
]

[ File changes (patch level 1)
	D = Deleted.
	M = Modified.
	A = Added.

	M The Forgotten Server.exe
	  data/
	M	global.lua
		XML/
	M		mounts.xml
	M		outfits.xml
]

[ Milestone (patch level 1)
	Added new outfits.
	Added more new munts.
	Removed outfits limit.
	Players with no vocation will no longer lose items on death.
	Players will now receive full health and mana on level advance.
	Fixed a crash related to summons and the new damage messages.
	Fixed client debugs when talking to NPC's.
	Fixed a bug in the sqlite schema and rebuilt the sqlite database.
	Fixed a bug with the loading of lastMotd.txt.
	Fixed selling in NPC trade window.
]

